      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and represents a solid, dependable choice for daily commuting. Mechanically, the engine and transmission are in good working order, ensuring a reliable drive. However, there are visible signs of wear consistent with its age, including several noticeable scratches on the exterior paint and some minor staining on the interior upholstery. It is an ideal car for someone prioritizing functionality and mechanical health over aesthetic perfection.",
